    "spell_type": "focus",
    "subtype": "spell",
    "text": "You howl with passion for your cause, empowering yourself to push beyond your limits. You gain a number of temporary Hit Points equal to your level and a +4 circumstance bonus to damage. If you reduce a fiend to 0 Hit Points during this duration, you regain a number of Hit Points equal to the creature\u2019s level.",
